text: "I Love Me" is a song by American entertainer Demi Lovato. It was released on March 6, 2020, as the second single from her upcoming seventh studio album. She co-wrote the song with Anne-Marie, Jennifer Decilveo, Sean Douglas, and its producers, Oak, Keith Sorrells, and Alex Niceforo. The song entered the Billboard Hot 100 at number 18. == References == Category:2020 songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Pop songs Category:Demi Lovato songs
